  <md:title>Appendix A: Preparing for licensure</md:title>
  <md:abstract>Case studies in educational psychology that deal with a realistic teaching problem or dilemma.</md:abstract>
  <md:uuid>3af7559a-4ec2-479d-9ec6-c38658588c3d</md:uuid>
